					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13381800#post-4665715</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13381800/scp-5852#post-4665715</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 27 May 2020 13:46:50 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>TheHouseOfBalloons</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3369416</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Honestly, I feel this piece kind of goes in many different directions without going into enough detail to really make me all that interested in any of them.</p> <p>I'm also not really sure why the tooth condition chart was included as none of that info was ever referenced again; the cicada mythos tie-in didn't really do much for me either and without any sort of real expansion on that group of stories it felt like a cheap callback. The addendum also doesn't add anything new storywise and just says; &quot;Now we know they spread through touch, so we don't touch them.&quot;</p> <p>-1, sorry. This has potential as an idea but you need to pick a storyline and run with it in more detail.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
